m/israeli-official-downbeat-on-prospects-for-hostage-release-deal-with-hamas/0000018e-9b55-dd2b-ad9f-db5f6ae00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的妻子将获得以色列纳税人资助的“私人美发沙龙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/netanyahus-wife-to-get-private-hair-salon-funded-by-israeli-taxpayers/0000018e-9ba2-dd2b-ad9f-dbfa64500000</link><description>以色列非官方第一夫人以“安全问题和高层威胁”为由，在总理耶路撒冷官邸附近租了一套空置公寓</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 22:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/netanyahus-wife-to-get-private-hair-salon-funded-by-israeli-taxpayers/0000018e-9ba2-dd2b-ad9f-dbfa64500000</guid></item><item><title>对伊朗和真主党的沉重打击：伊朗高级将军被暗杀标志着以色列北部战线的危险转折</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/iranian-generals-assassination-signals-a-dangerous-turn-in-israels-northern-front/0000018e-9b3f-d64e-afce-ffbf18780000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列和真主党一直小心翼翼地避免全面战争，但大马士革造成叙利亚和黎巴嫩圣城军指挥官死亡的空袭表明，以色列不断提高向北方对手索取的价格</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 20:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/iranian-generals-assassination-signals-a-dangerous-turn-in-israels-northern-front/0000018e-9b3f-d64e-afce-ffbf18780000</guid></item><item><title>“人们不断咒骂辛瓦尔”：反对哈马斯的加沙人确信他们是大多数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/people-are-cursing-sinwar-gazans-opposing-hamas-are-sure-theyre-the-majority/0000018e-9ada-dfd2-afce-deff025f0000</link><description>接受《国土报》采访的四名加沙人对加沙地带的哈马斯领导人以及 10 月 7 日发动战争的决定表示不满。他们说，许多人担心哈马斯会因为他们的言论而惩罚他们，并指责阿拉伯媒体在报道时视而不见。有人批评该团体</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/people-are-cursing-sinwar-gazans-opposing-hamas-are-sure-theyre-the-majority/0000018e-9ada-dfd2-afce-deff025f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在全麻下成功接受疝气手术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-undergoes-successful-hernia-operation-under-full-anesthesia/0000018e-9ad1-d64e-afce-fff5513b0000</link><description>据他的办公室称，内塔尼亚胡完全清醒，状况良好，并被转移到康复病房</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-undergoes-successful-hernia-operation-under-full-anesthesia/0000018e-9ad1-d64e-afce-fff5513b0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗誓言对以色列高级将领在大马士革被杀一事作出“严厉”反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/iran-blames-israel-for-syria-strike-threatens-harsh-response-for-killing-of-top-general/0000018e-9a50-d64e-afce-fff552490000</link><description>伊朗革命卫队表示，有七名革命卫队成员在袭击中丧生，而以色列拒绝就这一事件发表评论。这次袭击杀死了一名曾在黎巴嫩和叙利亚领导精锐圣城军的伊朗高级军事顾问</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 17:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/iran-blames-israel-for-syria-strike-threatens-harsh-response-for-killing-of-top-general/0000018e-9a50-d64e-afce-fff552490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 178 天：以色列逮捕哈马斯领导人哈尼亚的亲属</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-178-israel-arrests-relative-of-hamas-leader-haniyeh/0000018e-9a87-dd2b-ad9f-dadf84280000</link><description>据报道，以色列对伊朗大马士革大使馆的袭击造成六人死亡，其中包括革命卫队高级指挥官 ■ 以色列军队在两周行动后从 Al-Shifa 医院撤出 ■ 以色列和美国官员将就以色列国防军可能对拉法发动地面进攻举行虚拟会议 ■ 三人以色列南部地区发生刺伤袭击，以色列人受伤 ■ 战争结束 178 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-178-israel-arrests-relative-of-hamas-leader-haniyeh/0000018e-9a87-dd2b-ad9f-dadf84280000</guid></item><item><title>无人机袭击埃拉特的以色列海军基地；伊拉克亲伊朗民兵声称对此事负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/drone-strikes-idf-navy-base-in-eilat-pro-iranian-militia-in-iraq-claims-responsibility/0000018e-99f8-dd2b-ad9f-d9faa9c50000</link><description>军方表示没有人员伤亡，但基地内的一座建筑受到轻微损坏</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:17:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/drone-strikes-idf-navy-base-in-eilat-pro-iranian-militia-in-iraq-claims-responsibility/0000018e-99f8-dd2b-ad9f-d9faa9c50000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统的犹太人不会在一夜之间被强行加入以色列国防军，但变化即将到来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.highlight/ultra-orthodox-jews-wont-be-press-ganged-into-the-idf-overnight-but-change-is-coming/0000018e-99fe-dcec-a3ef-dbffd16e0000</link><description>犹太学院学生的兵役自动豁免期满之际，极端正统派社区正在发生重大变化。那些处于边缘的人逐渐意识到，必须真正融入以色列社会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.highlight/ultra-orthodox-jews-wont-be-press-ganged-into-the-idf-overnight-but-change-is-coming/0000018e-99fe-dcec-a3ef-dbffd16e0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其反对派对独裁者埃尔多安造成令人震惊的打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/turkeys-opposition-lands-authoritarian-erdogan-a-shocking-blow/0000018e-9a35-dd2b-ad9f-da7f48730000</link><description>周日晚上，土耳其书写了历史：反对派在地方选举中取得如此巨大的胜利，标志着埃尔多安下台的第一天，以及重建正常运转的民主的机会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/turkeys-opposition-lands-authoritarian-erdogan-a-shocking-blow/0000018e-9a35-dd2b-ad9f-da7f48730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列依靠武力，自取自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-israel-relies-on-force-it-sets-itself-up-for-suicide/0000018e-99e1-dd2b-ad9f-d9fb98760000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:43:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-israel-relies-on-force-it-sets-itself-up-for-suicide/0000018e-99e1-dd2b-ad9f-d9fb98760000</guid></item><item><title>“哈马斯喉舌”：内塔尼亚胡称赞允许他关闭以色列半岛电视台的新法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/netanyahu-pushes-ahead-law-for-immediate-shutdown-of-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018e-99f0-de2c-afff-bbf8be670000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡宣布他打算立即停止以色列境内“恐怖分子渠道”的活动，并声称该渠道参与了 10 月 7 日的大屠杀。白宫表示该法律“令人担忧”，并强调新闻自由的重要性</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/netanyahu-pushes-ahead-law-for-immediate-shutdown-of-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018e-99f0-de2c-afff-bbf8be670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方表示，对加沙的希法医院进行突袭可能会获得有关以色列人质的重要情报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-al-shifa-hospital-raid-may-yield-crucial-intel-about-hostages/0000018e-99a8-de2c-afff-bbe8d5ab0000</link><description>参加此次行动的以色列国防军高级军官表示，以色列军队发现了 10 月 7 日发生的事件的文件，可以提供有关加沙哈马斯扣押的以色列人质的信息</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 13:26:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-al-shifa-hospital-raid-may-yield-crucial-intel-about-hostages/0000018e-99a8-de2c-afff-bbe8d5ab0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的巴勒斯坦人像我一样不断游行以保护我们的土地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-palestinians-in-israel-like-me-keep-marching-to-protect-our-land/0000018e-996f-de2c-afff-bbef3b1f0000</link><description>土地日纪念 1976 年被以色列军队杀害的六名反对征用土地的手无寸铁的抗议者。我们绿线两侧的巴勒斯坦人仍然生活在它的遗产中。今年，一些人梦想着以色列重新占领加沙，这比以往任何时候都更加重要</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 13:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-palestinians-in-israel-like-me-keep-marching-to-protect-our-land/0000018e-996f-de2c-afff-bbef3b1f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人重新开始预订出国旅行。只是不要称之为假期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-are-back-to-booking-trips-abroad-just-dont-call-it-a-vacation/0000018e-98d7-d45a-a5be-b8d764ea0000</link><description>尽管战争仍在继续，机票价格也很高，但以色列人仍在计划逾越节及以后的航班。他们选择提供安全感的目的地，其中包括亚洲、美国和岛屿</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-are-back-to-booking-trips-abroad-just-dont-call-it-a-vacation/0000018e-98d7-d45a-a5be-b8d764ea0000</guid></item><item><title>“冲击议会！”耶路撒冷的大规模反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动要求采取更激进的措施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/storm-the-knesset-large-anti-netanyahu-protest-leaves-some-demanding-more-radical-steps/0000018e-9991-dd2b-ad9f-d9dbbf440000</link><description>数百个帐篷在耶路撒冷搭建起来，进行为期四天的抗议活动，示威者对政府即将进入春季休会感到愤怒，呼吁举行新的选举。但对于一些人来说，这是一个错失的机会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:36:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/storm-the-knesset-large-anti-netanyahu-protest-leaves-some-demanding-more-radical-steps/0000018e-9991-dd2b-ad9f-d9dbbf440000</guid></item><item><title>“我们无声”：记者向阿拉伯世界介绍以色列境内的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-are-voiceless-the-journalist-educating-the-arab-world-about-palestinians-in-israel/0000018e-94fe-d4de-afee-f4ff167b0000</link><description>出生于拿撒勒的穆斯塔法·卡布拉维 (Mustafa Qablawi) 最近搬到了约旦河西岸，从那里他开始接触世界各地的巴勒斯坦人，希望他们能够了解以色列的巴勒斯坦人面临的挑战，特别是自 10 月 7 日以来的挑战。“以色列的巴勒斯坦人是孤儿”。他告诉国土报</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-are-voiceless-the-journalist-educating-the-arab-world-about-palestinians-in-israel/0000018e-94fe-d4de-afee-f4ff167b0000</guid></item><item><title>希伯伦山区巴勒斯坦人生活的镜头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-lens-on-the-life-of-palestinians-in-the-hebron-hills/0000018e-9947-d764-adff-9fcffc3c0000</link><description>诺加·卡林斯基 (Noga Kalinsky) 在 Masafer Yatta 地区拍摄的照片捕捉到了约旦河西岸希伯伦南部山区的自然之美和巴勒斯坦人民的苦难</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 11:21:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-lens-on-the-life-of-palestinians-in-the-hebron-hills/0000018e-9947-d764-adff-9fcffc3c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>